q:"Which of the following is the correct sequence to form a coherent sentence or passage?\nP. The RBI announced a cut in the repo rate by twenty-five basis points.\nQ. This decision was taken after reviewing slowing GDP growth and benign inflation data.\nR. Banks are now expected to transmit this rate reduction to their lending rates.\nS. Borrowers with floating-rate loans stand to benefit if transmission is swift.",
